title: Egypt: Sisi, World Leaders Inaugurate New Suez Canal From Mahroussa Royal Yacht
text:
Kenya: Solar Power Installed at Dozens of Primary Schools 
Mahroussa Royal Yacht has arrived to Ismailia Governorate in order to participate in the inauguration of the New Suez Canal on Thursday 06/08/2015. 
The Royal Yacht "Mahroussa" was built in 1863 and participated in the inauguration of the Suez Canal in 1869. Egypt
